{"tid":1647231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單方法，被捕時唔出聲都話到比中知你係邊個！","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:40:23.000Z","uid":116560,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50e234c2929a568ef1ae664d02534a53cf44ca75","tid":1647231,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"就係寫係手上面，被捕時捲起衫袖比鏡頭影。<br />\n<br />\n就算雙手被綁，都可以手同身體摩擦，逐少逐少捲上去。<br />\n被捕時，大聲叫可能被打，又或者太驚、現場太亂都有可能聽唔清你個名。<br />\n寫既話，只要你既字大粒同清楚，遠鏡頭都可能影到。<br />\n唔知實用如何，但總叫減少被消失既機會。<br />\n<br />\n手邊只有幼身筆，用粗既酒精maker效果更佳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5t3n0uq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5t3n0uq.jpg&h=d3ae4475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8511dde8178965d816059ed38b768d3af7a5326d","tid":1647231,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:10:33.000Z","msg":"代表香港人 鼓励一众国内同胞 Chinese People Supporting 911 AGAIN<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646786</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"98a7417196a41d9aef4ecadaf75e35a1b24d2a46","tid":1647231,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望多個方法得知被捕手足們身份"},{"pid":"e6b78bd4208d022da2f12e91bbb2c423560993ac","tid":1647231,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"同我捽甩佢"},{"pid":"8d5aa36f1901872b092f2435217560f11fdab6b7","tid":1647231,"uid":277595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afb9a9020c23005b3be359dd405ecd59160fe98d","tid":1647231,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT